
Operations:
    add, edit, delete, complete, complete all, reopen, reopen all, clear completed

Contexts-filters:
    - all
        add
        edit
        delete
        complete
        complete all
        reopen
        reopen all
        clear
    - active
        add
        edit
        delete
        mark completed
        mark all completed
        clear
    - completed
        edit
        delete
        reopen
        reopen all
        clear

Additional operations:
    cancel edit by press Escape
    confirm edit by press Tab
    confirm edit by click outside
    delete by emptying text

General:
    -items left counting

Switching from filter to filters:
    -all
        active
        completed
    -active
        all
        completed
    -completed
        all
        active


